download the flashcards zip
install the open cards software
http://opencards.info/
learn how to use open cards there

To study for finals with these flash cards:
  create a folder for your cards
    right click the folder and select "add card set"
    add all the ppt slides from the zip
  select all of the ppt slides
  use the "last minute" option on open cards
  select "limit the number of cards to be learned"
  set to 3
    this means that you learn 3 cards from one ppt, then move on to the next
    after you finish all the slides, it will bring you back to the menu
    just run it again, it will remember which 3 slides you've already learned
